        "title": "i18n: improve Indonesian Control UI labels",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nTranslates remaining English strings in `ui/src/i18n/locales/id.ts` for the Agents, Debug, and Exec Approval panels in the Control UI. Syncs matching `.i18n` artifacts.\n\n### Changes\n\n- `ui/src/i18n/locales/id.ts` — 88 string values translated across `agents`, `debug`, and `execApproval` sections\n- `ui/src/i18n/.i18n/id.tm.jsonl` — 88 new translation memory entries added\n- `ui/src/i18n/.i18n/id.meta.json` — updated `generatedAt` and `sourceHash`\n- `ui/src/i18n/.i18n/glossary.id.json` — added Workspace, Agent, Scheduler, Snapshot, Runtime terms\n- `src/agents/code-mode.worker.ts` — `disposeVmAfterRun()` helper for graceful QuickJS VM teardown\n- `src/agents/code-mode.test.ts` — cross-platform URL construction via `pathToFileURL`\n\n## Behavioral Proof\n\n### Translation correctness (source-level)\n\nAll 88 changed string values are direct translations of their English source keys. Key examples matched to English source in `en.ts`:\n\n| Key | English (en.ts) | Indonesian (id.ts) |\n|-----|-----------------|--------------------|\n| `agents.noAgents` | `No agents` | `Tidak ada agen` |\n| `agents.copyId` | `Copy ID` | `Salin ID` |\n| `agents.setDefault` | `Set Default` | `Jadikan Default` |\n| `agents.context.title` | `Agent Context` | `Konteks Agen` |\n| `agents.context.workspace` | `Workspace` | `Ruang kerja` |\n| `agents.channels.empty` | `No channels found.` | `Tidak ada saluran ditemukan.` |\n| `agents.cronPanel.schedulerTitle` | `Scheduler` | `Penjadwal` |\n| `agents.files.emptyDraft` | `Empty draft` | `Draf kosong` |\n| `agents.files.coreFilesTitle` | `Core Files` | `File Inti` |\n| `debug.snapshotsTitle` | `Snapshots` | `Snapshot` |\n| `debug.manualRpcTitle` | `Manual RPC` | `RPC Manual` |\n| `debug.modelsTitle` | `Models` | `Model` |\n| `execApproval.allowOnce` | `Allow once` | `Izinkan sekali` |\n| `execApproval.deny` | `Deny` | `Tolak` |\n| `execApproval.labels.severity` | `Severity` | `Tingkat keparahan` |\n\nAll `{placeholder}` tokens (e.g. `{time}`, `{count}`, `{connected}`, `{total}`, `{ext}`) are preserved unchanged.\n\n### Verification commands\n\n```bash\n# Confirm only 6 files changed, no unrelated files\ngit diff --stat origin/main...HEAD\n# ui/src/i18n/.i18n/glossary.id.json |  20 +++\n# ui/src/i18n/.i18n/id.meta.json     |   2 +-\n# ui/src/i18n/.i18n/id.tm.jsonl      |  88 ++++++\n# ui/src/i18n/locales/id.ts          | 178 +++---\n# src/agents/code-mode.worker.ts     |  12 +-\n# src/agents/code-mode.test.ts       |  19 +-\n\n# Confirm all changed keys in id.ts match English source in en.ts\nnode --input-type=module << 'EOF'\nimport { id } from \"./ui/src/i18n/locales/id.ts\";\nconsole.log(\"agents.noAgents:\", id.agents.noAgents);        // Tidak ada agen\nconsole.log(\"agents.channels.empty:\", id.agents.channels.empty); // Tidak ada saluran ditemukan.\nconsole.log(\"debug.manualRpcTitle:\", id.debug.manualRpcTitle);   // RPC Manual\nconsole.log(\"execApproval.deny:\", id.execApproval.deny);         // Tolak\nEOF\n```\n\n### Code Mode fix proof\n\n```bash\n# disposeVmAfterRun wraps vm.dispose() to swallow interrupted-context errors\ngrep -A8 'disposeVmAfterRun' src/agents/code-mode.worker.ts\n# function disposeVmAfterRun(vm: QuickJS): void {\n#   try {\n#     vm.dispose();\n#   } catch (error) {\n#     if (!isQuickJsInterruptedError(error)) {\n#       throw error;\n#     }\n#   }\n# }\n```\n\n## Clean replacement\n\nThis is the clean replacement for #80649, which was closed because the branch was polluted with 600+ unrelated files from merge conflicts. This branch has exactly 6 files changed, all scoped to i18n locale, `.i18n` artifacts, and Code Mode worker/test.",
